{"tid":1303040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊做炸兩俠] 觀塘連儂牆事件整合，求證據！","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:58:24.000Z","uid":36423,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7da75511979136a268d2d7119ad74941bfcb4e93","tid":1303040,"uid":36423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:10:14.000Z","msg":"時間：2019年7月10日上午約9時至10時45分<br />\n人物：一名中國籍男子（附圖）<br />\n地點：觀塘道近路德會官塘書院下方行人隧道<br />\n事件：約上午9時，該名男子撕去貼於隧道內之一幅（連儂牆）告示。及後原地丟棄，懷疑違反《定額罰款(公眾地方潔淨罪行)條例》(第 570 章).<br />\n<br />\n約上午10時公開承認以上罪行，並向在場人仕表示需要報警處理其以上罪行。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場後聲稱被恐嚇，而否認以上罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即向在場人士呼籲，如果你於該段時間經過上述地點，而目擊上述事件發生經過，或者能提供錄影片段，請連絡觀塘警區提供證據。案件編號19025043,此案件編號由在場警員提供，並告知可按此編號索引至正式文件編號</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbvHpEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbvHpEr.png&h=7fe4a2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMR0bjt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMR0bjt.png&h=c4a4b95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MynKCZu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMynKCZu.png&h=a14a8402&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsK5nrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhsK5nrb.png&h=0be0b165&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAmzfMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAmzfMc.png&h=c0aabdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTvL6SU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTvL6SU.png&h=062488b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5asAMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5asAMi.png&h=05a32cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFit4EG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFit4EG.png&h=c2471179